readable.content: A black and white dog emerges from a yellow tunnel being coached by a man in a blue shirt at a dog show . A black and white dog is running out of a yellow tunnel with his trainer next to him . A black and white dog running from under a yellow cover with a person behind them . a man in a yellow and blue shirt behind a dog that is running out from under a yellow cloth . A small dog sprints away while its owner tries to catch it .
